REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CREEK_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Hudson's mission in Kowloon was accomplished. He had discovered Dragovich's end game. Nova 6. A nerve toxin so deadly, that if exposed you'd be dead before you hit the floor."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CREEK_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Dragovich's weapon."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CREEK_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Go back to Vietnam, Mason. Was Viktor Reznov still with you after you escaped from the MACV compound?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CREEK_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Ahh... Reznov was with me the whole time."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CREEK_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Are you sure?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CREEK_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7North, we went North. The Viet Cong. We were shot down. And Reznov even survived that!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CREEK_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Dragovich's lapdog Kravchenko was there. He knew we were comin'."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7No --"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Do not $&#* with me, Mason. I know when you're lying."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7'61. Bay of Pigs. What happened?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7[laughs] We all got killed."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7There's no use lying, Mason. We know you went in with Woods and Bowman."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Woods... And Bowman."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Dragovich. Do you remember Dragovich?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_CUBA_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Castro... We went in to kill Castro."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FLASHPOINT_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Executive order, Operation Flashpoint... Rip out the heart of their Space Program. Eradicate their long range missile project."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FLASHPOINT_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Take out the Ascension Group. Nazis, scientists, co-opted by the Russians after the war."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FLASHPOINT_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Sě... Aveva bisogno di sapere quello che avevano scoperto..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FLASHPOINT_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Operation 40 had planted a double agent working with the Ascension Group."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FLASHPOINT_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Grigori Weaver. His mission was to sabotage the rocket."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FLASHPOINT_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7But something went wrong Mason."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FLASHPOINT_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7I can't get these $&#**^% numbers out of my head!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Vorkuta. Reznov told me at Vorkuta."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7What did he tell you?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Mason... ascolta..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7It was a long time ago... Far away..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Dragovich, Steiner, Kravchenko... Devono morire tutti."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7...But he told me what they did."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7What kind of men they were..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_FULLAHEAD_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Why they all must die."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7The TET Offensive was the beginning of the end. When America really started losing the war."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Inside the MACV compound in Hue City, you established contact with the Russian defector."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7NO!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7We know you did. He turned himself in at MACV. You were there, Mason. He had intel on Dragovich. Everything. But it was a lost cause."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Shut the $&#* up!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7The NVA had surrounded the city.  MACV had all but burned to the ground. The defector was surely dead."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7He wasn't dead!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO19
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7It was a lost cause and you still went in - why?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_HUE_CITY_A_VIDEO20
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7His protection team had gone dark. I couldn't accept that he was dead. I needed that $&#**^% dossier!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_INT_ESCAPE_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Mason, amico mio... Dimmi..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_INT_ESCAPE_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7A cosa puoi credere ancora, quando vieni tradito da te stesso?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_INT_ESCAPE_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7When all that you are, all that you have done, is buried beneath the lies and the deceit of corrupt men."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_INT_ESCAPE_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7I will die in this wretched place... The only thing that keeps me alive is the thirst for Vengeance."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_INT_ESCAPE_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7They must be stopped, Mason."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_INT_ESCAPE_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Dragovich... Steiner... Kravchenko... All MUST die..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KHE_SANH_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Take us back again, Mason. After Baikonur, where did Washington send you next?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KHE_SANH_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Vietnam. $&#**^% Khe Sanh."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KHE_SANH_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7This was in 1968?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KHE_SANH_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Yeah. I was part of the SOG unit led by Frank Woods. It was recon on covert Russian activity in Laos."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KHE_SANH_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7What about your CIA handler, Hudson. Was he in Khe Sanh? Do you remember him there?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KHE_SANH_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Hudson... [laughs] Yeah. Mr. Shades. That guy was an ice cube."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7We have the dossier that the defector gave you at MACV."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7We've ID'd all of Dragovich's men. Kravchenko, Steiner, Clarke."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7You know them. Masterminds of Project Nova."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Nova 6. Reznov called it Nova 6."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Dragovich..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7What do you know about Doctor Clarke?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7We know that Clarke was the chemical engineer who helped formulated Nova 6. Malignant narcissist. Degenerate prodigy."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Your handler Jason Hudson was sent to Kowloon to interrogate Clarke. Do you remember?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO19
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Why keep asking? You already know everything."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO20
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7No Mason. We don't know what the numbers mean. We don't know where they're broadcast from."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_KOWLOON_A_VIDEO21
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Why don't you ask Hudson? Kowloon was his mission. He interrogated Clarke."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_PENTAGON_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7After your escape, you were assigned to Jason Hudson at the CIA. How could he trust you when he knew that Viktor Reznov helped you break out of Vorkuta?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_PENTAGON_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Reznov...was my friend...but he didn't make it out."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_PENTAGON_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Viktor Reznov was a communist. How did the CIA know you weren't compromised?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_PENTAGON_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7They tested me. They knew I wouldn't break and I won't break now."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_PENTAGON_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7The government wanted Dragovich. They wanted you to kill him."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_PENTAGON_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Yeah, and there were others. Others I was supposed to kill."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_PENTAGON_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Who? Who, Mason?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Dragovich has fully weaponized and deployed Nova 6. He has sleeper cell agents all over the US just waiting for the signal..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7[interrupts] We've been invaded."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7The US was invaded decades ago Mason. The communists have been waiting. Now they're ready to strike."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7What the $&#* am I supposed to do?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7You know about the sleeper cells..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7I'm trying to help you."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Dragovich uses number sequences to communicate with the sleeper cells. Those numbers are broadcast from one location, Mason."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Why the Hell do you think I know where it is?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO19
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7You were in Vorkuta, Mason. We know what happens at Vorkuta. They programmed you. You can translate the codes."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO20
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7But Reznov was never..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO21
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7STOP! Mason. We are on the brink of war. Where is the broadcast station? Where is the broadcast station?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO22
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Dragovich had us like rats in cages..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO23
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Mason! We're losing him."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO24
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7We are all brothers...we are all prisoners...Laos..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_POW_A_VIDEO25
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7He's gone."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_REBIRTH_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Dragovich's sleeper cells are on US soil. Nova 6 is weaponized. They will use it. Moscow has gone dark. We are out of options. A pre-emptive strike on Russia is prepared. The President WILL authorize."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_REBIRTH_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Mason! For the last time! Where is the numbers station?!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_REBIRTH_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7How many times!... Steiner was at Rebirth Island. We had to kill Steiner."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_REBIRTH_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATORE: ^7\"Noi\"? Tu e Viktor Reznov?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_REBIRTH_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Volevamo la stessa cosa. La stessa."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_REBIRTH_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7We're losing him again. Aw, God... He's back at Rebirth."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7You were in the Mekong, heading North to Kravchenko's compound. You were heading for Laos."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Laos... Kravchenko... The $&#**^% psycho was spraying nerve gas all over Vietnam. I had to kill him! Do you understand? I have to kill 'em all."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Laos! Mason! You were heading up the Mekong River into Laos. You received word from Jason Hudson. What did he tell you?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7My handler, Hudson."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7The CIA downed a Soviet cargo plane carrying Nova 6. It... It went down in Laos. Our SOG team went in."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7What happened?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO19
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7I...keep...hearing...the $&#**^%...numbers..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_RIVER_A_VIDEO20
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7It's a broadcast, Mason. The broadcast."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_SO_NARRATIVE5_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATORE: ^7Hai ucciso Kravchenko. Hai distrutto la loro base. Mason?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_SO_NARRATIVE5_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATORE: ^7Woods e Bowman sono stati uccisi. L'intera squadra SOG spazzata via. Solo tu sei sopravvissuto, Mason. Tu e basta."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_SO_NARRATIVE5_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7No, Reznov surivived."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_SO_NARRATIVE5_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATORE: ^7Solo tu, Mason."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_SO_NARRATIVE5_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7No, Reznov č ancora con me... da Vorkuta."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7We are in grave danger from the communists. Our freedom... Our very way of life is at risk."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1DRAGOVICH: ^7Il piano per colpire al cuore l'Occidente č in movimento."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Bisogna fermarlo, Mason."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MCNAMARA: ^7He has no fear. No conscience. No weakness."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1STEINER: ^7Dragovich ha agenti dormienti sparsi per tutta l'America. Aspettano solo un segnale per rilasciare la Nova 6."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7I'm told that you are the very best that we have. Anywhere."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Dragovich... Kravchenko... Steiner..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7You will need to be."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO19
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7These 'men' must die..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_UNDERWATERBASE_A_VIDEO20
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7Mr. Mason..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Why didn't Castro just kill you? Why did he give you to Dragovich?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Cause, Castro and Dragovich were working together."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Eh... You were a gift."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Eh... Right..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATORE: ^7Dove ti ha portato Dragovich?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Vorkuta...had to fight...just to survive."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7What happened in Vorkuta, Mason?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7I was on my own -- almost a year."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO19
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Think, Mason...what did they do to you?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_VORKUTA_A_VIDEO20
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7I'd given up hope of ever getting out...but Viktor Reznov found a way."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATORE: ^7Jason Hudson ha guidato l'attacco a Yamantau."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_A_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7Yeah. 20 degrees below zero. $&#**^% ice cube was in his element."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_B_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7You were captured by Dragovich a second time. Your unit was MIA in Laos, presumed dead. Your handler, Hudson, had no choice but to continue the hunt for Nova 6 without you --"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_B_VIDEO12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7He went to Mt. Yamantau -- $&#**^% Soviet doomsday bunker --"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_B_VIDEO13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7That's right. A fully operational military complex buried deep in the Ural Mountains."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_B_VIDEO14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7That's where Hudson was contacted by Friedrich Steiner -- the Nazi scientist that developed the initial strain of Nova 6 for Dragovich --"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_B_VIDEO15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7Hudson learned about the numbers there. The broadcasts -- I've been there, Mason. I've been to the Yamantau complex."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_B_VIDEO16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MASON: ^7My God... The numbers are REAL..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_WMD_B_VIDEO17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1INTERROGATOR: ^7They've always been real, Mason. This isn't a game. We face annihilation unless you cooperate. Where is the broadcast station?!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7For time and the world do not stand still. Change is the law of life. And those who look only to the past or the present are certain to miss the future."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD12
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7I said, 'are certain to miss the future'!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD13
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CASTRO: ^7[laughs] Cońo... I missed that."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD14
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MCNAMARA: ^7Prime Minister Castro, this missile crisis was the last straw. We almost blew ourselves up. Now we invited you here today..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD15
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7In good faith!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD16
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MCNAMARA: ^7...in good faith, to sort this thing out."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD17
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CASTRO: ^7And why is he here? He lost!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD18
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7As I always say, forgive your enemies, but remember their names. "

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD19
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7Now gentlemen, as I like to think, in the long history of the world, that there are only a few generations..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD20
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1NIXON: ^7Sounds like someone breaking in..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD21
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7Just the storm, Dick. Sit down."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD22
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1NIXON: ^7Oh my God!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD23
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MCNAMARA: ^7It appears the Pentagon has been breached."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD24
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7Zombies. Gentlemen, at times like these our capacity to retaliate must be and has to be massive, to deter all forms of aggression."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD25
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7Gentlemen, lock and load!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD26
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CASTRO: ^7Viva la Revolucion."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD27
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1MCNAMARA: ^7Any last words, Mr. President?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD28
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1NIXON: ^7Yes Jack, any superlative words of inspiration for your humble troops?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_PENTAGON_A_LOAD29
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1KENNEDY: ^7Do not pray for easy lives, my friends. Pray to be stronger men."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_THEATER_A_VIDEO11
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1RICHTOFAN: ^7[disturbo radio] Commento 741021!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_ZOMBIE_THEATER_A_VIDEO12
